target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE4<tab>ごらんあれ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Here.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE5<tab>これで、いいっしょ？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Take it, take it!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE6<tab>ほんの気持ちですが、受け取ってください。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>My only regret is that I could not return sooner.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>これでいかがっ？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Go on, dearie, take it!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>これで満足だろ？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>'Twas a most profitable venture, I'd say.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>今回の成果です。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Always a pleasure to serve, and so on and so forth.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>気に入ってもらえると、うれしいですの。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>You're welcome.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>これで満足かしら？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>Some of my finest work yet!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>がんばりました～。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE1<tab>It is an honor to serrrve, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE1<tab>お気に召すかな?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE2<tab>I await your orders, <var 08 E905 ((miss)) ((sir)) /var>!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE2<tab>これじゃ足りないかい？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE3<tab>...
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE3<tab>……受け取れ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Why don't we both take it easy for a while?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE4<tab>こんなもんで、どう？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE5<tab>And with that, we can move on to more important matters.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE5<tab>文句は言わせないよ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Was it everything you hoped it would be?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE6<tab>君へ贈るよ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>Your goods, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sirrr)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>どんなもんよ！？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Just what ye wanted, am I right?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>さぁ、これでいいだろ？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>Thank you for your patronage.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>これぐらい大したことないんだから。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Can I go now?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>これで精一杯です……。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>And that's the end of that chapter.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>お気に召すかにゃ？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>I hope you like it...
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>がんばったにゃん！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>If you require aught else, you need only ask.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>また、いつでもご依頼ください。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Bwahahaha!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>文句はいいっこなしだぜぇ？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>Here.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>受け取れ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Why don't we toast our success with a pint or two?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>日頃の行いの表れだな。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>If you want, I can undertake another one right now.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>オイラ、がんばっただろ！？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>It's all there, chief. Ye have me word.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>全力尽くしたぜ！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab><var 08 E905 ((Milady)) ((Milord)) /var> is satisfied, I trust?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>今回の成果を見てよ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>A good haul, all in all.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>ありがたく受け取りなっ！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>A pleasure as always.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>これでいいだろ？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Hope you're godsdamned happy.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>心ばかりの品ですが、受け取ってください。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>You yourself could do no better.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>ワタシに頼って、正解だったな！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>That ought to do it.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>粗品ですが、どうぞ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_AURA_MALE_TYPE1<tab>I pray that you are pleased with the result, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_AURA_MALE_TYPE1<tab>そらよ！
どーんと仕入れたぜ！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_AURA_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Bet you weren't expecting <var 1A 02 /var>that<var 1A 01 /var> now, were you?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_AURA_MALE_TYPE2<tab>次回の結果も、期待してろよ！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_AURA_MALE_TYPE3<tab>Ah, for the days when ventures were a gentleman's pursuit...
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_AURA_MALE_TYPE3<tab>クックック……今宵の哀れな贄だ……。
受け取るが良い……。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_AURA_MALE_TYPE4<tab>If you don't mind me saying, I think I did rather well.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_AURA_MALE_TYPE4<tab>こんなものでどうだい？
お前さんが喜んでくれたら嬉しいなぁ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_AURA_MALE_TYPE5<tab>I will be expected to do this again, I gather.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_AURA_MALE_TYPE5<tab>ほらよ。
……別に、お前のためにとってきたんじゃねーからな。

source:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_AURA_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Can I survive this overbearing,♪
Or live a life of mad despairing,♪
My proffered goods despised, rejected?♪
No, no, it's not to be expected!♪
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_AURA_MALE_TYPE6<tab>フッフッフ……皆まで言うな。
我が主の喜びは、十分に伝わっているからなッ！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>I live to serve, <var 08 E905 ((my lady)) ((my lord)) /var>.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>……お気に召しましたか？
その品が、<var 08 E905 ((お嬢様)) ((旦那様)) /var>に幸せを運んできますように！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>All's well that ends well, wouldn't you say?
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>へっへー！　これくらいは楽勝さ！
あー、いい汗かいたッ！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>There it is.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>受け取りなさい。
これが、あなたの望んだ冒険の成果よ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>All acquired in accordance with local laws. <wink> <wink>
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>どうぞどうぞ、納めてくださいな～。

source:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>Alright, take yer shite and quit leerin' at me arse.
...What? Ye can't seriously expect me to humor yer fetishes all the time, can ye?
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>これで……いいんだよね？
何かあったら、ごめんね……。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>Hardly my finest work, but I'm not ashamed to say I did it.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>ね、あたしに頼んで正解だったでしょ～？
ちゃんと一生懸命やってるんだから～、顔に出ないだけ！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Only the best for you, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE1<tab>どうかな、気に入ってくれるといいんだが。
……自信はあるぞ？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE2<tab>This is what you asked for, yes? So take it.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE2<tab>……ほらよ。
こんくらい、ワケねぇぜ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE3<tab><var 1A 02 /var>Here<var 1A 01 /var>.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE3<tab>フン、満足か？
何のこれしき……児戯に等しい！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Here's what you wanted! And, er...let us focus on the <var 1A 02 /var>what<var 1A 01 /var> and not talk about the <var 1A 02 /var>how<var 1A 01 /var>, yes?
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE4<tab>やぁやぁ、なかなかいい旅だったぞ。
主殿にも、成果を見てほしいな。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Bahahaha! How do you like <var 1A 02 /var>this<var 1A 01 /var>!?
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE5<tab>おらよッ！　どうだッ！
仕事はいつでも、完璧ピカピカにこなす主義だからな！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Look what I brought, just for you!
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE6<tab>こんなもんでどうっスかね？
オレ、結構ガンバったつもりなんだけど！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>I do hope it pleases you.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>どうかしら？
ハニーが気に入ってくれると、アタシも嬉しいわ♪

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Behold! This is what you seek, yes!?
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>どーよ？
さっさと感謝の言葉を聞きたいもんだね！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>I believe this is what you sought of me.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>汝の望みは、満たした。
我の望みもまた、果たしてくれような？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>The deed is done. <yawn> Now, time for a rest...
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>むにゃ……はやく寝たいから、がんばったよぉ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>Well? Do you like it? Oh, say that you do!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>ボクに任せておけば間違いないって、言ったろ？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>Behold the fruits of my labor! I do hope it is everything you expected.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>今回の成果ですの！
きっときっと、ご満足いただけると思いますわ！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_VIERA_MALE_TYPE1<tab>I trust this meets with your satisfaction, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>? After all, your contented smile is my greatest reward!
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_VIERA_MALE_TYPE1<tab>成果を披露させてくれるかい？
キミの役に立てることが、ボクの至上の幸せなんだ！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_VIERA_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Does that meet with <var 08 E905 ((her ladyship)) ((his lordship)) /var>'s approval? (It bloody better...)
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_VIERA_MALE_TYPE2<tab>おらおら、どうッすか？
<var 08 E905 ((姉貴)) ((兄貴)) /var>の期待に応えてぇっす！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_VIERA_MALE_TYPE3<tab>No need to thank me, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>. Fulfilling one's duty is its own reward.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_VIERA_MALE_TYPE3<tab>礼には、及びませぬ。
これぞ私の喜びなれば……。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_VIERA_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Not bad, eh? In fact, I think we should pop a cork to celebrate!
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_VIERA_MALE_TYPE4<tab>おれの頑張り、どおよ？
く～っ、これで気持ちよく酒が呑めるぜ！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_VIERA_MALE_TYPE5<tab>This is what you wanted, yes? I told you I'd take care of it.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_VIERA_MALE_TYPE5<tab>ほ～ら、これでイイでしょ？
オレの仕事なんだから、トーゼン。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_VIERA_MALE_TYPE6<tab>And there you have it, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>─all wrapped up like a Hatching<var 1F /var>tide gift basket.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_VIERA_MALE_TYPE6<tab>どうでしょ、主さんに御満足いただけるかな？
それが、あっしの仕事でございますからね。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Do you require aught else, <var 08 E905 ((Mistress)) ((Master)) /var>?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>追加の用件ですか？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Ye know I'm in the middle o' yer venture, don't ye?
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>おう、冒険中に呼び戻すとは、
さぞや重要な話だろうなぁ？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>What is it?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>……用か？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>What now? I'm busy.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>はいはい、何か言い忘れたことでもありましたか？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>I trust there is a reason for this interruption?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>さらに仕事を積もうってのか……？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>I came as quickly as I could! What is it?
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>なんか用？
俺、冒険中だけど……。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>Yes, my <var 08 E905 ((lady)) ((lord)) /var>?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>どうされましたか……？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Somethin' else, love?
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>呼びもどすなんて、穏やかじゃないね？
何かあったのかい？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>Well? What is it?
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>あなたのために冒険をしている最中よ。
追加の業務連絡なら、手短にね。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>You couldn't have picked a more inconvenient time.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>ごめん、まだ冒険中……って、追加の仕事？
なんだ、よかった。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>This better be worth my time.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>遠慮せず、何でも言いなさい。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>What is it, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>? Something urgent?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>なになに、どうしたの！？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>You have additional orders, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>何か問題でも！？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Tell me you ain't got somethin' else for me, chief!
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>貴様のために冒険をしているというのに、
呼び戻すとは何事だ？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>You have interrupted my venture. Proceed.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>何か、粗相でもございましたか？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>I'm here now, so...
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>ひと休みしてたところでした。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>You interrupt my task. Why?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>冒険中なんだが……男は黙って、俺様参上。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Apologies for the delay, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>冒険中に、また君に会えてうれしいよ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab><var 08 E905 ((Milady)) ((Milord)) /var> has another task for me?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>呼び戻すなんて、何かあった？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>I'm a little busy, but what is it?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>何か、困ったことでも？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>Was there something else?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>いかがなさった？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Summons? <var 1A 02 /var>Now<var 1A 01 /var>? Well, if you insist.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>参りましたぁ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>You do know how this works, right? You assign me a venture and then leave me to my task.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>なになに、どうかした～？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>Missed me, didn't you?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>急に呼び戻すなんて、どうかした？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Hail to thee, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>. Your humble servant has set aside his task and hastened to your side.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE1<tab>わわ、何かありましたか！？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Why'd ye call me back from me venture, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE2<tab>おっと、何か忘れたことでもあったかい！？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE3<tab>This really isn't the best time.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE3<tab>俺の冒険を邪魔するとは、いい度胸だな？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE4<tab>I thought you were going to let me do this my way?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE4<tab>ぜひにおよばず。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE5<tab>What!?
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE5<tab>冒険中に呼びだしとは……
おれが依頼を投げ出してもいいってことか？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE6<tab>I'm back, I'm back!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE6<tab>飛んで戻ってきたよ！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>How may I serve you, <var 08 E905 ((Mistress)) ((Master)) /var>?
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>どうしました！？
急用ですかっ！？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Did somethin' 'appen, dearie?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>呼び戻すなんて、急用でもできたのかい？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>What's all this, then? Another chance for mischief?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>どうかしましたか？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab><yawn> Just so you know, I was busy carrying out your tasks.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>私のこと、呼びましたの？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>This had better be important.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>追加のお願いを聞いてあげます。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>Whaaat is it?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>何なりと、いいつけてください～。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE1<tab>I have rrreturned, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE1<tab>どうかしたのかな？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE2<tab><var 08 E905 ((Miss)) ((Sir)) /var>, you mustn't interrupt a soldier when he's on a mission!
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE2<tab>冒険中に呼び出すなんて、
そんなに俺様の顔が見たかったのか？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE3<tab>...
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE3<tab>……何事だ？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE4<tab>You would burden me with additional tasks?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE4<tab>新しい仕事かな？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE5<tab>I thought I asked you to leave me to my task?
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE5<tab>冒険中に呼び出すとは……
俺に文句でもあるのかな？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE6<tab>You require additional services?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE6<tab>ちょうど君のことを考えてたところだったんだ！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>Forgive me, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sirrr)) /var>, but your catcall comes at an inopportune time.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>さらに仕事の話？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Damn, just when I was startin' to enjoy meself!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>冒険中のアタシを呼び戻すなんて……いい心がけね？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>A cat must be allowed to focus on her task.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>もう、何か用！？
あたし、忙しいんだけど……。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>You know I've not finished the venture yet, rrright?
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>あのぉ……
追加の仕事でもありましたかね……？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>Mind explainin' what this is about?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>何かあったかにゃ？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>You know, you shouldn't summon me when I'm in the middle of a venture!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>お仕事中に、もっと仕事にゃん？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Did you require aught else, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>言い忘れたことでもありましたかな？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Bwahahaha! Ye need somethin' else?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>気になることは、何でもいってみぃ！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>I've returned. What is it now?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>冒険者よ、心配事でもあったのか？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Yeah? I was just enjoyin' a pint of─hic─uh, venturin'.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>不測の事態でも起きたのか？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>I've already got my hands full with this venture, but what is it?
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>呼び戻されるなんて、
オイラ、何かヘマしたか？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>What else ye need, chief?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>全力帰還！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>I am at <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>'s beck and call.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>何か用かい？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>What'll it be, cap'n?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>冒険中だぞ、まだ何か用なのか！？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab><var 08 E905 ((Madam)) ((Sir)) /var>?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>フン、さらに仕事を押し付けるつもりか……？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Godsdammit, what now?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>不備でもありましたか？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>I do not take kindly to interruptions.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>呼び戻すとは何事だ！？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>Dammit, <var 08 E905 ((woman)) ((man)) /var>, did ye forget I was out on a venture?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>さらなる仕事とは、身に余る光栄。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_AURA_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Is aught amiss, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>?
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_AURA_MALE_TYPE1<tab>おぉ？　なんだなんだ？
気にかかることでもあったのか？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_AURA_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Something on your mind, <var 08 E905 ((miss)) ((mate)) /var>?
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_AURA_MALE_TYPE2<tab>呼び戻すとは、いい度胸だぁ！
遠慮は無用、なんでも言いな！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_AURA_MALE_TYPE3<tab>I have a life outside of <var 1A 02 /var>you<var 1A 01 /var>, you know.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_AURA_MALE_TYPE3<tab>貴様……！
我輩の狩りの興を削ぐか……無礼者！！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_AURA_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Let me tell you, it was absolute chaos out there. Quite frankly, I'm lucky to be alive! But I heard your call, and I knew I had to answer.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_AURA_MALE_TYPE4<tab>ちょうど、一息ついていたところだったんだよ。
なにか、困ったことでも起きたかい？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_AURA_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Worried about your venture? Don't be. Or have you some other reason for summoning me?
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_AURA_MALE_TYPE5<tab>ああ！？　ンだよ！！
仕事中に呼び出しって……何かあったんじゃねーだろうな！？

source:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_AURA_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Fair moon, to thee I sing,♪
Bright regent of the heavens,♪
Say, why is everything♪
Either at sixes or at sevens?♪
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_AURA_MALE_TYPE6<tab>それほど早急に会いたかったか！？
ハッハッハ、実は俺もだ！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab><var 08 E905 ((My lady)) ((My lord)) /var>. Is there aught else you require?
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>は、はいっ、只今！
<var 08 E905 ((お嬢様)) ((旦那様)) /var>、どうかなさいましたか？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Can't say I was expecting this. What can I do for you?
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>いちいち呼び戻すんじゃないよ、まったく！
アタイがいないと、何にもできないんだからさっ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>Do tell.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>冒険の途中に呼び出しとは、人使いが荒い主ね。
……構わないわ、用件を言いなさい。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Now, before you go jumping to conclusions, I'd just like to─ Oh! What can I do for you?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>なにか問題でもございましたか～？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>I-It's not like I was slaving away to make you happy or anything.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>あの……ごめんなさい……！
え……怒られるんじゃないの……？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>Somethin' else I can do for you, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>? Don't hold back now.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>どうしたの？　なにかあったの？
出かけてたのに……あっ、ごめん、本音が出ちゃった。
……って、それがダメなのか！　ごめんごめん♪

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE1<tab>If there is something else you would have me do, you need only say the word.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE1<tab>おっと、急用か？
何かあったら、またいつでも呼んでくれ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE2<tab>I am here. I don't have to be happy about it.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE2<tab>……フン。
テメーに呼ばれて、来ないワケにいくかってんだ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE3<tab><var 1A 02 /var>Yes<var 1A 01 /var>?
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE3<tab>一度出た狩り場から、きびすを返させるなど……。
貴様でなければ、無事では済ませんところだぞ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Phew! Glad you got me out of <var 1A 02 /var>that<var 1A 01 /var>─er, never mind. What can I do you for?
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE4<tab>おやおや、何か急用かな？
ひと休みしてたところなんだけど……。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Gahahaha! Couldn't wait to see you, myself!
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE5<tab>おいおいおい、どうしたってんだ！？
あんまりドキッとザワッとさせんじゃねーぞ！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Well, that was awfully sudden! You truly cannot get enough of me, can you?
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE6<tab>急に呼ばれてビビったわ！
なんスか、何でも困ったこと聞きますけど？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>I was hoping you would call, love.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>んもぉ、ナニナニ？
アタシじゃなくっちゃ、聞いてあげられないコト？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>What is the matter? Why do you summon me back so soon!?
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>ったく、わざわざ呼び戻したからには、
アタシじゃないと無理な話なんだろうね？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>I trust there is a good reason for this interruption?
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>いかなる僻遠からも駆けつけよう。
この両の耳が、汝の我を呼ぶ声を拾う限り。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab><yawn> You do know I was in the middle of something...yes?
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>ふわぁ……お呼びとあらば、なんなりとぉ……。
一度帰ってこれたってことはぁ、お昼寝していーい？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>What is it this time? I was just beginning to have some fun...
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>このボクを呼びつけるなんて！
……お前じゃなきゃ、許さないぞ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>You frightened me, <var 08 E905 ((Mistress)) ((Master)) /var>! Is something the matter!?
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>いかがしましたの！？
わたくし、飛んで戻ってまいりましたのよ！
貴方様が乞い願ったのですから！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_VIERA_MALE_TYPE1<tab>I rushed back as soon as I heard your call. You have need of my services?
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_VIERA_MALE_TYPE1<tab>おやおや、どうかしたのかい？
大切なキミのためなら、いつでも駆けつけるとも！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_VIERA_MALE_TYPE2<tab>I'm a bit sodding busy, yer <var 08 E905 ((ladyship)) ((lordship)) /var>. Ye get mud on yer shiny boots, or summat?
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_VIERA_MALE_TYPE2<tab><var 08 E905 ((姉貴)) ((兄貴)) /var>、どうしたんすか！？
自分が戻ったからには、任しときやがれッての！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_VIERA_MALE_TYPE3<tab>Was there something else, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>...?
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_VIERA_MALE_TYPE3<tab>他ならぬ主よりの任でございます。
道行きを戻すもまた、主のためのみ……。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_VIERA_MALE_TYPE4<tab>What is it? What's wrong? ...Aside from me missing my favorite barstool?
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_VIERA_MALE_TYPE4<tab>なになに、どしたの～？
慌てて戻ったから、酔いも覚めちまったよぉ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_VIERA_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Yes? This is interfering with <var 1A 02 /var>your<var 1A 01 /var> venture, just so you know.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_VIERA_MALE_TYPE5<tab>よくも途中で呼んでくれたよなぁ～？
……心配して、帰ってきちゃったじゃん。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_VIERA_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Is something amiss? Or did you simply miss <var 1A 02 /var>me<var 1A 01 /var>?
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER2_VIERA_MALE_TYPE6<tab>おや、いかがしました？
もしや……あっしの顔でも見たくなったかな？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>I shall return to my duties forthwith.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>それでは、冒険に戻ります！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Right, then. Back to it.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>用が終わったのなら、冒険に戻るぞ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>If you would excuse me.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>行くぞ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>If there's nothing else...
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>ぼちぼち冒険に戻りますね。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>I shall return to <var 1A 02 /var>your<var 1A 01 /var> work.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>やれやれ、冒険に戻るぜ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>You've got it!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>ほんじゃ、また行ってくる。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>Pray excuse me, my <var 08 E905 ((lady)) ((lord)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>では、冒険の続きに戻りますね。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>I'd best get goin'.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>さて、気を取り直して行ってくるよ！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>Excuse me.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>仕切りなおして、冒険に戻るわ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Guess I'll get back to that venture you assigned me.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>それじゃ、いってきまーす。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>That was not worth my time.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>成果を期待してなさい。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>I'll take care of it, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>, don't you worry!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>それじゃ、冒険に戻りま～す。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>As you wish, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>いつでも、呼んでください。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Don't forget that I'm busy with this venture o' yours, chief!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>では、戻るぞ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>I must go.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>では、冒険に戻ります。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Sure, sure.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>はぁ、冒険に戻らないとですよねぇ……。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>I have work to do.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>男は黙って、再出発。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Understood, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>! Oh, and fear not─the venture shall be completed on time!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>僕は行くけど、何かあったら、いつでも呼びなよ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>I shall carry out <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>'s wishes to the best of my ability.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>大したことなくて、よかった。
また行くわね。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>We finished? That venture's not goin' to finish itself.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>また冒険に出るけど、
何かあったら、いつでも呼んで。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>All right, then.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>改めて、出陣なり！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>If you would excuse me, I have a venture to finish.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>いざ、冒険にぃ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>Unless it is urgent, do not summon me during a venture again.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>それじゃ、いってくるね～！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>Are we finished already? Oh...
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>私の帰りを待っててね。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Do not hesitate to call on me again, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE1<tab>結果を、お楽しみに！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE2<tab>I'll do what I can, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE2<tab>冒険再開だ～！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE3<tab>Back to my venture, then.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE3<tab>用は済んだか？
ならば、俺は行くぞ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE4<tab>I can't keep runnin' back to see you during these ventures, you know.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE4<tab>かならずや、功をあげてごらんにいれます。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Fine.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE5<tab>冒険に戻ってやるよ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE6<tab>I'll go, I'll go!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE6<tab>依頼の仕上げに取りかかるよ～！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>As ever, it is an honor, <var 08 E905 ((Mistress)) ((Master)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>いい結果を出せるよう、がんばりますっ！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>So much to do, so little time!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>それじゃ、また冒険に戻るよ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>We'd best see to our respective tasks, eh?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>成果が出るまで、もう少し待っててください。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Don't summon me, I'll summon you.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>がんばってきますの！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab><sigh> I am not getting paid enough for this.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>気を取り直して、いってきます。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>We'll talk again soon!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>いってまいります～。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE1<tab>If there is naught else, I will rrresume my venture.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE1<tab>それじゃ、また行ってくるね。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Once more, unto the breach!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE2<tab>俺様は行くけど、さびしがんなよ？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE3<tab>...
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE3<tab>……出る。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE4<tab>I suppose you want me to finish the venture too, don't you? <sigh>
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE4<tab>しばしのお別れだね。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Pray do not disturb me until the venture is complete.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE5<tab>これでまた、気ままな冒険に戻れるよ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Patience, my good <var 08 E905 ((woman)) ((man)) /var>. Your venture will be finished in due time.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE6<tab>名残惜しいけど……
君のために、がんばってくるね。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>I shall rrreturn to my venture, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sirrr)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>任せておいて。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>The wilderness calls to me, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>それじゃ、行くわね。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>Farewell for now.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>あたし、すっごく忙しいけど……
いつでも呼びもどしていいんだからねっ！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>I told you I'd take care of it, so stop worrying.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>あのぉ……
とりあえず冒険の続きに戻ります……。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>Is that all? Hmph.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>冒険が終わるまで、もうちょっとだけ待っててにゃ～。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>...Try as I might, I can't stay mad at you.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>冒険再開にゃん。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Beg your pardon, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>, but I must needs return to my venture.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>冒険が終わるまで、もう少し待っててください。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Bwahahaha! Back to me venturin'!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>俺の帰りを、心待ちにしていろよ！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>I must go now.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>冒険者よ、また会おう。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Now then, if ye'll─hic─excuse me, I've got a venture what needs doin'!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>達者でな。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>All right. Let me handle it.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>オイラ、がんばるからな！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Happy to be of service, chief!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>全力再出発！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>Understood, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>さぁ、冒険へ戻るよ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Ye still want me to carry out that venture, too, eh? Just checkin'.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>よっしゃ、また冒険に戻るよ！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>Acknowledged.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>フン、冒険の続きに行ってやるよ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>'Fore you ask, I've not forgotten about the venture.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>出直します。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>If you want quality work, then leave me be.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>行ってくるぞ！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>Now then, where was I...
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>何かあったら、
いつでもお呼びたてください。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_AURA_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Then if you would excuse me, I should return to my venture.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_AURA_MALE_TYPE1<tab>よし、もう心配事はないな！
また何かあったらすぐ呼んでくれ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_AURA_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Right, then. I ought to be getting back to that thing of yours. “Venture,” was it...?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_AURA_MALE_TYPE2<tab>心機一転で、また出発だぁ！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_AURA_MALE_TYPE3<tab>We shall meet again, old friend. But now I must steal away into the night.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_AURA_MALE_TYPE3<tab>フン……わかれば良い。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_AURA_MALE_TYPE4<tab>If I don't make it back, I just want you to know... Eh, the hells with it. I'll tell you next time.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_AURA_MALE_TYPE4<tab>もう、大丈夫だな。
さぁて、うまいものとお前さんが望むものを探しに戻ろう。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_AURA_MALE_TYPE5<tab>As you wish...<var 08 E905 ((Mistress)) ((Master)) /var>.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_AURA_MALE_TYPE5<tab>ったく、急に呼び出すんじゃねーよ……。
そんじゃ、また行ってくらぁ。

source:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_AURA_MALE_TYPE6<tab>I must wander to and fro;♪
But wherever I may go,♪
I shall never be untrue to thee!♪
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_AURA_MALE_TYPE6<tab>では、任務に戻るとしよう。
完遂の暁には、大いに誉めそやすがいいぞ！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab><var 08 E905 ((My lady)) ((My lord)) /var>.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>もうよろしいですか？
では、私も引き続き、がんばって参りますね！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>I suppose you'll be wanting me to finish that venture too, yes? Right, right. Don't know why I bothered asking...
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>もー少ししたら、ちゃんと帰ってくるからさ！
いい子にして待ってな！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>Hmm.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>もういいかしら？
それなら、私は冒険に戻るわ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Right, so, if anyone asks, I wasn't here, agreed? Cheers.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>ではまた、仕切り直します～。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>Go on, then. Go. It's not like I haven't more important things to do or anything.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>じゃ……行くね……。
とりあえず、ごめんね……。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>Hm, hm. You've really nothin' else to ask? If you say so, then.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>それじゃ、冒険に戻るよ。
寂しがったってしらな～い、ばいば～い！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE1<tab>I am ever at your beck and call, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE1<tab>またいつでも呼んでくれ。
<var 08 E905 ((嬢ちゃん)) ((ダンナ)) /var>を困り顔のままにしておけないからな。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Don't expect me to play errand boy for you forever.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE2<tab>……テメーの用事はそんだけか？
心配すんな、また呼びな。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE3<tab><var 1A 02 /var>Enough<var 1A 01 /var>.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE3<tab>ほかに伝え残したことはないか？
俺様は行く……獲物が待っているのでな。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE4<tab>If there's nothing else, I'll be getting back to...er, what was it again? Oh, yes, the venture!
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE4<tab>それなら、もう行くよ。
えーと、仕事はどこまで終わったんだったかな。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Gahahaha! Back to work for me!
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE5<tab>大丈夫なら、またシゴトに戻るからな。
バビュンと飛ばしてくるぜ！！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Are you sure you don't want to spend more time with me? Ah, but I jest!
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE6<tab>オッケー？　もうダイジョブ？
へへっ、そしたらまた行ってくるんで！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>If ever you're feeling lonely, I am but a ring of the bell away.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>それじゃ、また行ってくるわね♪
でも、寂しくなったらいつでも呼んで、ハニー♪

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>I am off! At least until you call me back again...
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>それじゃ、アバよ！
ま、呼ばれりゃ、戻ってきてやるけどさ……。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>The road calls me again.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>それが汝の、望みのすべてか。
なれば我はまた、与えられし旅に戻ろう……。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab><yawn> I really could use a nap...
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>いつでもお昼寝休憩、大歓迎だよ～♪

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>Well, back to the grind! I do hope you appreciate all this!
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>それじゃ、依頼をこなしてきてあげる。
帰ってきたら、ちゃーんとボクのこと、褒めてよね？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>If that is all, I shall return to my task. Ah, the joy of adventure!
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>それではもう一度、行ってまいりますわね！
嗚呼、わたくしの旅路に実り多からんことを！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_VIERA_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Are you certain? If needs be, I can return at a moment's notice!
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_VIERA_MALE_TYPE1<tab>もう大丈夫かい？
困り事があったら、すぐにボクを呼ぶんだよ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_VIERA_MALE_TYPE2<tab>If that'll be all, I'll get back to that other thing ye asked me to do.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_VIERA_MALE_TYPE2<tab>心配しねェで待っといてください！！
大船に乗ったつもりで、ッてやつすね！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_VIERA_MALE_TYPE3<tab>If you've no further need of me, I shall return to my assigned task.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_VIERA_MALE_TYPE3<tab>済みましたか。
いざ再び、私は私の戦野へ……。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_VIERA_MALE_TYPE4<tab>I'll head back out, then. Duty first, debauchery second!
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_VIERA_MALE_TYPE4<tab>はいよ～、またあとでね！
戻ったら一緒に、乾杯しようぜ！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_VIERA_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Hmph. You're sure that's everything? I'd rather not be running back and forth, if it's all the same to you.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_VIERA_MALE_TYPE5<tab>フン……もう大丈夫なんだろうなぁ？
旅の途中で気にしてやったり、しねーから！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_VIERA_MALE_TYPE6<tab>I really must be on the road again. Pray no harm befalls my soft, furry hide!
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_VIERA_MALE_TYPE6<tab>それじゃあ、また行って参りましょう。
旅道中の無事でも、祈っておいておくれよ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>It pleases me to inform you that the venture is complete.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>きっちり、やり遂げました。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Hey, I finished that venture o' yours.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>今、戻ったぞ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>It is done.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>帰った。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Well, that was exhausting...
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>なんとか冒険を達成しました。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Your venture is finished.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>くたびれたぜ……。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Guess what I finished!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>いっちょあがり～！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>My <var 08 E905 ((lady)) ((lord)) /var>, the venture you bid me undertake has been finished.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>ご依頼どおり、やりとげました。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>I've got your goods, by the way. Let me know when you want 'em.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>やりきったよ！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>I have something for you.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>やるだけやったわよ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Thank the gods that's over.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>ふぅ……働いたなぁ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>My venture report is ready.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>終わったわよ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>Good news, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>! The venture was a success!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>ただいま～。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE1<tab><var 08 E905 ((Madam)) ((Sir)) /var>, your venture is complete.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>精魂こめて取り組みました。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Got somethin' for you, chief!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>戻ったぞ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>I have come with your goods.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>ご依頼を果たしてまいりました。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>I took care of that venture for you.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>はぁ～、ひとりで冒険に出るより、
あなたと話してるほうが落ち着きますね。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>You wish to hear my report?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>男は黙って、依頼完了。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Ahhh, now that was fun!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>ただいま、会いたかったよ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>I come with good tidings, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>無事に帰ってきたわよ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>This about the venture? I took care of it.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>ひと仕事終えて、気分爽快。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>There you are! I've brought what you requested.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>任務完遂。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Oh, it's you. I suppose you'll want to hear about the venture.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>精進しましたぁ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>Let's get on with it, shall we?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>たっだいま～！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>I've been waiting for your summons.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>がんばってきたよー。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Hail to thee, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>. You shall be pleased to hear that the venture was a success.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE1<tab>ただいま、戻りました！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE2<tab>You want this stuff now or later?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE2<tab>帰ったぞ！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE3<tab>I'm finished.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE3<tab>帰ってきたぞ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Been a long time comin', but the venture's finally finished.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE4<tab>これにて、らくちゃく。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Whew.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE5<tab>いや～、疲れた、疲れた～。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE6<tab>I did it, I did it!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE6<tab>やり遂げたよ～！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>Does <var 08 E905 ((Mistress)) ((Master)) /var> wish to hear my report?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>お仕事終わりましたっ！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>'Ello, dearie. I reckon you want your goods?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>依頼は、やり遂げたぞ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>My pockets are bursting with your goods!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>ようやく、仕事が終わりました。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Well, this was to be expected. The venture, yes?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>ただいまですの！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>We should talk about the venture.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>無事に帰ってきました。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>I'm baaack!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>戻りました～。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE1<tab>My rrreport is rrready, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE1<tab>ただいま。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Mission accomplished, <var 08 E905 ((miss)) ((sir)) /var>!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE2<tab>戻ってきてやったぞ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE3<tab>...
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE3<tab>……戻った。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE4<tab>May I leave after making my report? No? <sigh>
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE4<tab>お待たせしました。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE5<tab>I have prepared a formal report.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE5<tab>た、だ、い、ま。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Am I to deliver my report now, or shall we discuss other matters first?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE6<tab>ようやく、君にまた会えたね。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>This cat has brought you a present, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sirrr)) /var>...
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>戻ったわよ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Ye want to hear the whole story, or just read the report?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>さぁて、任務完了だ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>'Twas naught more than a rrroutine task.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>戻ってきてあげたわよ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>I did my very best, just like I said.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>あのぉ……
なんとか戻ってきました。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>Everythin' you need to know is in the report.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>ただいまにゃ～！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>I have so much to tell you!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>帰ったにゃん！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>I have brought that which you desire, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>無事に冒険が終わりました！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Bwahahaha! That venture was an <var 1A 02 /var>ad<var 1A 01 /var>venture, let me tell ye!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>今帰ったぜぇ！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>The venture is complete.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>できるかぎりのことはしてきた。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Venture? What in the seven hells are ye─ Oh, the <var 1A 02 /var>venture<var 1A 01 /var>! Aye, I did that.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>冒険を終えた達成感は、格別だな。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Got a delivery for you. Just say the word.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>オイラ、がんばってきたぞ！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Hey, chief! I got what ye asked for!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>全力帰還！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>I have what <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var> requested in my possession.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>全力つくしたよ！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>I've got the goods, cap'n!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>終わった、終わった～！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>Venture complete, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>フン、帰ってきてやったぞ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Took a while, but the venture's done.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>只今、帰還しました。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>I had a mind to summon <var 1A 02 /var>you<var 1A 01 /var>, actually.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>ひと仕事おえたぞ！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>This venturin' business ain't so bad!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>只今、戻りました。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_AURA_MALE_TYPE1<tab>It pleases me to inform you that the venture is complete.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_AURA_MALE_TYPE1<tab>帰ってきたぞ、<var 08 E905 ((お嬢)) ((旦那)) /var>！
俺からの贈り物だ！　受け取ってくれ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_AURA_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Guess what I've got for you! No, really. Guess!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_AURA_MALE_TYPE2<tab>全力尽くしてきたぞ！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_AURA_MALE_TYPE3<tab>I renew my objection to that pointless endeavor. Informally now and by affidavit later.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_AURA_MALE_TYPE3<tab>かしずけ！　我輩の帰還だ！
さあ……存分にもてなすが良い！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_AURA_MALE_TYPE4<tab>You know, I think I'm starting to get the hang of this.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_AURA_MALE_TYPE4<tab>ただいま戻ったぞ。
はい、お前さんへの土産だ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_AURA_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Per your orders, I have completed the venture...<var 08 E905 ((Mistress)) ((Master)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_AURA_MALE_TYPE5<tab>たでーま帰りましたよ……っと。

source:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_AURA_MALE_TYPE6<tab>For he himself has said it,♪
And it's greatly to his credit,♪
That he is a retainer!♪
He remains a retainer!♪
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_AURA_MALE_TYPE6<tab>会いたかったぞ、我が主よ！
さあさあ、成果のお披露目とゆこうではないかッ！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>I have seen to the venture, <var 08 E905 ((my lady)) ((my lord)) /var>.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>お声がかかるのを、お待ちしておりました！
お勤め、無事に完了しております。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Oh, the tales I could tell you about that venture...
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>チョチョイと、終わらせてきたよ！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>I've finished.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>帰ったわ。
あなたが選んだ私だもの、報告は不要でしょう？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Heh, didn't expect him to put up such a─ Oh! Just the <var 08 E905 ((woman)) ((man)) /var> I was hoping to see!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>ただいま、帰ってまいりました～。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>I-It's not like I risked life and limb to bring you back shiny baubles or anything.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>ただいま……ごめんなさい……。
ごめんねばかりで、ごめんね……。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>Oh, it has been a day such as you wouldn't believe!
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>おかえり！
……じゃなかった、ただいまだ～！　えへへっ♪

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Rest assured that I spared no effort in doing your bidding, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE1<tab>帰還したぞ。
<var 08 E905 ((嬢ちゃん)) ((ダンナ)) /var>に報告するのが、待ちきれなかったんだ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE2<tab>This is all you will get from me. I hope it satisfies you.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE2<tab>帰還したぞ。
オレの仕事ぶりを知って驚くなよ？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE3<tab><var 1A 02 /var>Done<var 1A 01 /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE3<tab>貴様が命じたこと、みな果たした。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE4<tab>I'm back! Now, do you want the good news or the bad news?
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE4<tab>帰ってきたよ。
えーと、主殿に何から話すべきかな……。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Gahahaha! Feast your eyes on this!
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE5<tab>ほーらよ！
バッチリガッツリ、キメてきたぜ！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Guess who's returned with a tale to tell? Why, <var 1A 02 /var>me<var 1A 01 /var>, of course!
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE6<tab>ウーッス、ただいま！
オレのカッコイイ武勇伝、聞いてくれるっスよね！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>I have returned, love. And do I have a tale to tell...
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>帰ったわ、ハニー♪
ウフフ、アタシの冒険譚、聞いて聞いて♪

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Hah! Now <var 1A 02 /var>that<var 1A 01 /var> was a venture for the ages!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>くーっ！　アツい冒険してきたぜッ！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>There are places I would rather be, yet here I am. Be grateful.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>旅路を巡り、また帰る場所。
それが汝の元であること、我の喜悦となろうぞ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab><yawn> Oh...that's right. I had something to tell you.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>ふわぁ～…………。
帰ってキミの顔見ると、すぐ眠くなっちゃうねぇ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>I've returned! Come now, are you not happy to see me?
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>ほーら、ボクのご帰還だぞ！
……早く、おかえりは？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>I could scarcely wait to return to your side, <var 08 E905 ((Mistress)) ((Master)) /var>!
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>ただいま帰りましたわ！
嗚呼、お会いしとうございました！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_VIERA_MALE_TYPE1<tab>I am returned! And I have come bearing a gift.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_VIERA_MALE_TYPE1<tab>会いたかったよ、ただいまっ！
キミにプレゼントを用意してきたんだ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_VIERA_MALE_TYPE2<tab>About damn time! My ears were twitching summat fierce listening out for that bell...
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_VIERA_MALE_TYPE2<tab>へへッ、耳がヒョコヒョコ疼いちまってました。
<var 08 E905 ((姉貴)) ((兄貴)) /var>に会えるのが待ちきれなくッて……！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_VIERA_MALE_TYPE3<tab>I believe this concludes your venture, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>...
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_VIERA_MALE_TYPE3<tab>主よりの用命、確かに満たしたかと……。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_VIERA_MALE_TYPE4<tab>I have returned, and gods have I worked up a thirst! Oh, and this is for you!
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_VIERA_MALE_TYPE4<tab>ただいまぁ～っと……はい、コレ！
あんたに、オ・ミ・ヤ・ゲ、だよ！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_VIERA_MALE_TYPE5<tab>I did what you asked. You'll be wanting my full report, then?
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_VIERA_MALE_TYPE5<tab>……ただいま～。
アンタに聞かせたい話が、ゴマンとあるんだ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_VIERA_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Wait until you see the goods I got my paws on!
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER3_VIERA_MALE_TYPE6<tab>なかなか景気のいい土産を用意してきましたよ。
あっしには主さんの笑顔が一番の駄賃だが、どうかな？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_PIXIE_1<tab>Oh, my adorable sapling! You have need of <var 29 EA02 /var>, yes? But sing the word, and let your beautiful branch do what only they can.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ENTER_PIXIE_1<tab>あら、あなたの美しい枝を呼んだかしら？
<var 29 EA02 /var>への用件があるなら、
私におまかせなのだわ！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_PIXIE_1<tab>A whispered word, and off goes <var 29 EA02 /var> on a grand adventure! What wonders await at journey's end?
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_ACCEPT_PIXIE_1<tab>夢見る<var 29 EA02 /var>にささやきかけて、
冒険の旅へといざなってあげる……。
きっといい旅になるのだわ！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_PIXIE_1<tab>Carried by the wind, the leaf flutters to the ground─and so does <var 29 EA02 /var> return to your side. Was the journey a fruitful one?
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_COMPLETE_PIXIE_1<tab>風に乗って、あなたの葉……
<var 29 EA02 /var>が舞い戻ったようね。
旅の成果には、満足できたのかしら？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_PIXIE_1<tab>You have no more need of <var 29 EA02 /var>? So be it! I shall steal quietly from your loyal servant's dreams.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE_PIXIE_1<tab>もう用件は済んだのかしら？
それじゃあ、<var 29 EA02 /var>の夢から、
そっと抜け出すのだわ……起こさないように、ね。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_PIXIE_1<tab>Very well. I shall slip quietly from <var 29 EA02 /var>'s dreams. May your leaf flutter, float, and find a way back to you.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_LEAVE2_PIXIE_1<tab>それじゃあ、<var 29 EA02 /var>の夢から、
そっと抜け出すのだわ……。
あなたの葉が、無事に舞い戻りますように！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_EQUIP_PIXIE_1<tab>From verdant green to glittering gold, so does the leaf take on delightful hues with each new season. If you would see <var 29 EA02 /var> dressed in new colors, your beautiful branch will attend to the task.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERBELL_00544_EQUIP_PIXIE_1<tab>季節が巡れば、葉もまた色づく……。
<var 29 EA02 /var>の装いを変えたいのなら、
私が手伝ってあげるわ！
